==Other work==
Due to his Lebanese background, he was named one of the AFL's multicultural ambassadors during the 2017 season.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/afl/teams/melbourne/christian-salem-hoping-for-better-luck-in-season-2017/news-story/6f54263844620f96c0a4b65eaf0d6e99|title=Christian Salem hoping for better luck in season 2017|last=Wood|first=Lauren|date=14 March 2017|work=Herald Sun|publisher=News Corp Australia|accessdate=9 November 2017}}</ref>

